input.activity_signal: Company appears inactive based on: 1) Only single FCC filing from 2020-07-23 with no recent activity, 2) Privacy policy page found at whisl.com suggests past web presence, 3) Most significantly, multiple 2024-2025 news articles show Whisl Telecom, LLC being targeted in "Operation Robocall Roundup" by attorneys general for illegal robocall activities, indicating regulatory enforcement action against the company
